Description classe: Abstract class for Look Up Table (LUT)

Description (EN): Array of operating point values of size (N,5) with N the number of operating points (Speed, Id, Iq, Torque, Power). OP values are set to nan if they are not given.
Rotation direction of the stator phases (phase_dir*(n-1)*pi/qs, default value given by PHASE_DIR_REF)
